WEBVTT

01:52.080 --> 01:53.120
Ji.

02:13.040 --> 02:14.120
Ji.

02:15.600 --> 02:18.520
I can see now. I can see now.

02:23.240 --> 02:24.080
Ji.

02:27.120 --> 02:28.160
Ji.

02:32.000 --> 02:33.440
Ji.

02:42.080 --> 02:43.120
Ji Ling.

02:44.320 --> 02:45.240
Ji Ling.

02:57.680 --> 03:00.720
Changsheng. Have you seen Ji Ling?

03:30.480 --> 03:31.360
BRING HEALTH…

03:31.440 --> 03:34.720
GATHER THE ESSENCE OF THE UNIVERSE
TO SHIELD ALL MAGICAL HARM

03:39.760 --> 03:41.200
"A dragon scale

03:43.080 --> 03:44.520
banishes all curses

03:46.400 --> 03:47.640
and misfortunes…"

03:48.760 --> 03:51.440
"…shields the spirit,
and restores life from death.

03:52.600 --> 03:57.440
However, it settles only upon
the one it deems worthy."

04:15.720 --> 04:16.839
Wu.

04:18.000 --> 04:22.400
To kill Jiu Ying, you must die.

04:26.240 --> 04:29.560
But the dragon scale
can bring you back to life.

04:31.760 --> 04:36.240
However, not everyone can bear its power.

04:37.720 --> 04:41.440
But you've been through
countless rewinds with Lonescale's power,

04:42.080 --> 04:44.400
creating a tie with the dragon scale.

04:45.640 --> 04:48.760
Maybe that's what it means
to be the fated one.

04:49.920 --> 04:54.280
Your heart was once occupied
by Jiu Ying's spirit fragment.

04:56.400 --> 04:57.840
From now on,

04:58.760 --> 05:03.560
let my dragon scale reside in your heart

05:06.080 --> 05:07.640
and stay with you forever.

05:11.280 --> 05:12.720
Don't be sad.

05:14.360 --> 05:15.600
Don't cry.

05:18.040 --> 05:19.640
I'll always be with you.

05:23.320 --> 05:27.040
Whatever you want, I'll bring it to you.

05:28.520 --> 05:31.560
You'll offer your heart if I want it?

05:32.840 --> 05:33.760
Yes.

05:40.120 --> 05:43.520
You like Ji Ling. I like him, too.

05:44.520 --> 05:50.000
I've always liked my past self.

05:52.440 --> 05:57.160
So even if there is no future,
there's nothing to regret.

05:58.920 --> 06:00.480
But you are different.

06:02.160 --> 06:04.160
You hate your past.

06:05.120 --> 06:07.840
You never enjoyed a moment of happiness.

06:10.000 --> 06:12.760
So, Wu,

06:14.440 --> 06:19.000
you deserve
a bright future more than I do.

07:37.960 --> 07:39.400
Ji.

07:43.960 --> 07:45.280
Ji.

08:40.440 --> 08:41.760
He's dead.

08:43.600 --> 08:46.800
Finally, he's free.

08:48.640 --> 08:50.080
I have to go now.

08:55.400 --> 08:56.880
Who are you?

08:59.560 --> 09:01.240
I told you.

09:04.080 --> 09:05.560
I am you.

09:07.360 --> 09:08.760
You are me.

09:10.120 --> 09:13.440
We are Yuan Wuhuo's
unfortunate obsessions.

09:16.000 --> 09:20.880
I've always wanted to be
your older brother and protect you.

09:22.040 --> 09:24.080
But many times,

09:25.400 --> 09:26.560
I thought

09:27.840 --> 09:31.800
you were supposed to be
a carefree little fox.

09:35.960 --> 09:40.320
I hoped you could be freed from
the shackles of the Dragon Deity's throne.

09:41.760 --> 09:44.600
I got you trapped here.

09:51.920 --> 09:54.080
What gives me the right

09:56.360 --> 09:58.000
to be your brother?

10:00.960 --> 10:02.800
I haven't achieved

10:04.400 --> 10:08.000
anything I wanted

10:10.480 --> 10:13.640
to achieve in my life.

10:16.560 --> 10:20.800
Before Yuan Wuhuo died,
he had only two obsessions.

10:20.880 --> 10:24.000
One was to protect his brother forever.

10:24.520 --> 10:30.000
The other was to free
Ji Ling from the lies.

10:32.520 --> 10:35.320
The good and evil twin
six-eyed butterfly demons

10:36.080 --> 10:38.920
devoured Yuan Wuhuo's physical form

10:39.440 --> 10:41.680
and absorbed his two obsessions.

10:42.960 --> 10:47.960
Two completely different beings
of good and evil split apart.

10:50.480 --> 10:52.720
That is, you and me.

10:54.360 --> 10:58.720
Li Jie and the butterfly demon Yuan Wuhuo.

11:01.880 --> 11:07.880
I tried everything to kill him
and free him from his endless pain.

11:10.080 --> 11:13.200
You tried your best
to protect the Dragon Deity.

11:17.920 --> 11:21.840
We are nothing
but the obsessions of a dying man.

11:21.920 --> 11:22.760
No.

11:29.360 --> 11:30.320
No.

11:32.920 --> 11:34.880
I may have come to Ji Ling

11:35.480 --> 11:37.920
because of the obsession.

11:40.680 --> 11:44.560
But all these years,
I've witnessed his glory, pain,

11:45.640 --> 11:48.680
mercy, and loneliness.

11:49.200 --> 11:52.640
All this has nothing to do
with you or the obsession.

11:53.920 --> 11:58.440
I did my best to serve the Shilin Sect

11:58.960 --> 12:02.120
out of my own will.

12:03.920 --> 12:05.040
Very good.

12:07.720 --> 12:10.720
But the person
you want to protect has died.

12:12.240 --> 12:16.320
Now, who are you going to live for?

12:18.680 --> 12:23.080
Figure out the answer yourself.

12:23.600 --> 12:26.880
My obsession has already been fulfilled.

12:27.640 --> 12:28.920
He's dead.

12:29.720 --> 12:31.240
He's free.

12:32.120 --> 12:33.640
Now I have to go.

12:36.320 --> 12:38.440
The person I want to protect

12:40.880 --> 12:43.480
is waiting for me across the river.

13:26.840 --> 13:28.600
Father. Mother.

13:30.160 --> 13:31.600
-Father. Mother.
-Brother.

13:31.680 --> 13:33.800
-You're back.
-I missed you.

13:35.040 --> 13:36.680
Xizai, you've grown so tall.

13:37.840 --> 13:40.600
Brother. Have some. It's still warm.

13:40.680 --> 13:41.760
Give Xizai one.

13:41.840 --> 13:42.760
Come on.

13:42.840 --> 13:44.640
-I've eaten.
-What?

13:46.040 --> 13:48.560
Mother's dumplings. Try it.

13:49.720 --> 13:51.840
You've lost weight. Try it.

13:51.920 --> 13:54.240
Come on. Eat more.

13:54.320 --> 13:56.240
Gain some weight. Be like me.

13:56.320 --> 13:57.360
Look at me.

14:38.160 --> 14:39.600
So this is the Formless Moon.

14:40.120 --> 14:41.840
What celestial air.

14:42.440 --> 14:44.960
Breathe it in,
and I'll live 500 more years.

14:45.040 --> 14:47.680
But why does it feel so cold?

14:52.040 --> 14:53.680
Traitor to the Formless Moon.

14:53.760 --> 14:55.760
How dare you bring someone here?

14:56.520 --> 14:59.160
-Why are you here?
-To destroy the Oracle Stone.

14:59.760 --> 15:01.400
Destroy the Oracle Stone?

15:02.040 --> 15:04.640
Wu Wangyan. Are you crazy?

15:04.720 --> 15:08.120
The Sacred Spring doesn't lie.
Memories don't lie.

15:08.200 --> 15:13.040
I came back to tell you the entire truth.

15:59.720 --> 16:04.120
Jiu Ying's spirit fragment
has been hiding in the Oracle Stone.

16:04.200 --> 16:08.000
Jiu Ying has integrated his spirit
with the Oracle Stone.

16:09.480 --> 16:12.120
The stone's power is everlasting,

16:12.200 --> 16:15.680
which sustains Jiu Ying's spirit.

16:16.280 --> 16:18.320
To kill Jiu Ying,

16:18.920 --> 16:22.360
we must destroy the Oracle Stone.

16:22.440 --> 16:24.000
THE OLD DRAGON FALLS
THE NEW DRAGON RISES

16:24.080 --> 16:25.800
HEAVEN AND EARTH TREMBLE
CHAOS FILLS THE WORLD

16:25.880 --> 16:27.520
AN OLD SOUL RETURNS AGAINST TIME
A NEW MOON RESHAPES THE WORLD

16:28.800 --> 16:32.160
This is the new prophecy.

16:33.240 --> 16:36.280
"The old dragon falls.
The new dragon rises.

16:36.360 --> 16:39.080
Heaven and earth tremble.
Chaos fills the world.

16:40.000 --> 16:43.400
An old soul returns against time.
A new moon reshapes the world."

16:44.480 --> 16:47.520
But nobody knows what it means.

16:57.800 --> 17:01.280
What's wrong?
We're finally destroying this stone.

17:01.360 --> 17:03.120
Isn't that a good thing?

17:03.200 --> 17:05.720
Why do you guys look unhappy?

17:07.760 --> 17:08.839
-It's nothing.
-It's nothing.

17:13.040 --> 17:14.920
More and more like a married couple.

18:36.040 --> 18:37.320
Finally,

18:39.560 --> 18:41.400
Jiu Ying is taken down.

18:43.360 --> 18:46.880
Master Dragon Deity would be happy, right?

18:49.640 --> 18:50.800
For so many years,

18:52.000 --> 18:55.880
he's been absorbing the dark power
from those possessed

18:56.600 --> 18:58.360
by Jiu Ying's spirit fragments

18:59.480 --> 19:02.360
to shoulder the pain for those people.

19:05.840 --> 19:08.640
I want to see my grandson again.

19:12.760 --> 19:15.480
Despicable Dragon Deity.
So what if you wipe me out?

19:16.320 --> 19:17.560
I am Jiu Ying.

19:17.640 --> 19:19.920
I am immortal.

19:21.960 --> 19:26.080
Too bad he won't be able to see this.

20:37.800 --> 20:41.680
These fancy garments
have always been the worst curse.

20:42.280 --> 20:45.720
People burdened with longing
carry an empty tomb in their hearts.

20:46.280 --> 20:48.360
Inside the tomb,
no bones, just the clothes.

20:50.160 --> 20:51.560
This is life…

20:53.200 --> 20:54.720
You silly fox.

20:55.880 --> 20:57.800
Didn't you spend a lifetime

20:59.000 --> 21:01.400
wearing someone else's garments?

21:03.280 --> 21:06.880
Some people are destined
to be like two mountains,

21:06.960 --> 21:09.200
gazing across vast grasslands,
across canyons,

21:10.120 --> 21:12.080
across a distance
that can never be closed,

21:12.680 --> 21:14.800
watching over each other.

21:14.880 --> 21:18.120
What are they waiting for?

21:18.200 --> 21:20.160
They're waiting for the snow.

21:21.200 --> 21:25.400
All it takes is a snow
for them to be both crowned in white,

21:25.960 --> 21:27.760
as if they had grown old together.

21:30.360 --> 21:31.200
Hey.

21:32.920 --> 21:34.960
We've grown old together.

22:59.480 --> 23:00.560
Thank you, Master.

23:02.920 --> 23:04.760
Bless us, Master Dragon Deity.

23:04.840 --> 23:10.680
I didn't expect that the story
started here and ended here too.

23:12.000 --> 23:13.760
I wanted to kill the dragon.

23:14.400 --> 23:15.640
But now,

23:18.280 --> 23:19.680
I've become the dragon.

23:21.680 --> 23:24.200
Master Dragon Deity.
Thank you for blessing me.

23:24.280 --> 23:25.480
These are all for you.

23:28.880 --> 23:30.240
Now you're obligated.

23:30.320 --> 23:33.440
It seems that you have
to protect the commoners

23:33.520 --> 23:34.920
for the rest of your life.

23:37.960 --> 23:39.520
Thank you, Master Dragon Deity.

23:40.160 --> 23:42.240
Do you think he is the Dragon Deity?

23:42.320 --> 23:43.320
Look.

23:43.400 --> 23:45.160
Even the demon hunter commander
is standing behind him.

23:45.240 --> 23:46.600
He must be the Dragon Deity.

23:46.680 --> 23:48.600
He will bless everyone.

23:48.680 --> 23:50.080
-Yeah.
-Right.

23:53.520 --> 23:55.240
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

23:55.320 --> 23:56.640
Thank you, Master Dragon Deity.

24:11.800 --> 24:13.680
Humans are better than demons in one way.

24:14.360 --> 24:15.600
When a human dies,

24:16.560 --> 24:20.560
people set a tombstone
and honor their memory.

24:21.440 --> 24:25.280
But when a demon dies,
they are gone without a trace.

24:26.320 --> 24:27.400
If…

24:29.400 --> 24:30.720
I mean,

24:32.320 --> 24:37.800
if I can have a tombstone after I die,

24:40.520 --> 24:42.120
I would wish for the name on my tombstone

24:44.000 --> 24:46.960
to change my surname from "Ji"
meaning a vessel,

24:49.080 --> 24:50.360
to a common family surname "Ji".

24:51.600 --> 24:53.360
I want to be remembered.

24:54.000 --> 24:55.200
I want to be mourned.

24:56.600 --> 25:00.800
I don't want to be
nothing more than a spirit vessel.

25:02.840 --> 25:03.880
Rest assured.

25:04.440 --> 25:05.880
I'll protect you.

25:06.880 --> 25:08.440
I won't let you die.

25:30.440 --> 25:32.440
Master Ji Ling sacrificed himself.

25:32.520 --> 25:35.280
We shall inherit his legacy
and guard the world.

25:36.560 --> 25:38.000
Master Ji Ling.

25:38.080 --> 25:39.440
I'll always remember

25:39.520 --> 25:43.200
the day you helped Luo'an City
dispel the Fox-Allure Spell.

25:43.280 --> 25:44.880
The sky looked amazing.

25:44.960 --> 25:46.520
Master Ji Ling.

25:46.600 --> 25:48.920
Are you free now?

25:49.000 --> 25:50.400
I'm happy for you.

25:50.480 --> 25:51.800
-Master Ji Ling.
-Master Ji Ling.

25:51.880 --> 25:54.360
To me, you will always
be the Dragon Deity.

26:00.640 --> 26:01.640
Ji Ling.

26:06.520 --> 26:08.480
You will never be forgotten.

26:34.480 --> 26:37.000
Every time I came to this room,

26:38.680 --> 26:41.480
I took a new puppet.

26:51.960 --> 26:55.400
We only had to put
this heart stone in its chest

26:57.600 --> 27:00.760
to get a brand new Ji Ling.

27:22.400 --> 27:25.760
Again and again.

27:42.160 --> 27:45.360
I should already be used
to your death by now.

27:57.160 --> 27:58.240
But now,

28:01.280 --> 28:03.000
you're gone for real.

28:09.600 --> 28:11.960
You said you wanted a tombstone.

28:13.520 --> 28:16.920
So, I'll bury this heart stone with you

28:18.240 --> 28:20.360
and make you a tombstone

28:21.920 --> 28:23.960
engraved with Ji Ling's name.

28:28.280 --> 28:30.080
"Spirit Memorial."

28:41.160 --> 28:42.560
Dragon Deity's Power.

28:47.560 --> 28:48.800
Master Chi Wen.

28:50.760 --> 28:53.920
This is the last strand
of Dragon Deity's Power I left behind.

28:55.040 --> 28:59.280
This heart stone contains
all the memories of Ji Ling.

29:00.040 --> 29:02.280
I'll take it to the Dragon Abyss,

29:02.360 --> 29:06.400
bathe it in the Sun and Moon
to absorb the universe's essence.

29:06.920 --> 29:09.880
Maybe after thousands of years,

29:10.920 --> 29:14.840
this heart stone can form
a shape through cultivation.

29:30.520 --> 29:34.080
Thousands of years?

29:38.520 --> 29:40.000
I can't wait that long.

29:57.920 --> 30:02.320
From now on, there are dragons once more.

30:04.640 --> 30:06.160
Jiu Ying has fallen.

30:06.680 --> 30:08.440
The mortal world regained peace.

30:08.520 --> 30:10.400
To the former Dragon Deity,

30:11.440 --> 30:13.760
my brother, Chi Wen.

30:23.840 --> 30:28.200
The former Dragon Deity was Ji Ling.

30:46.320 --> 30:47.520
Don't blame him.

30:50.080 --> 30:51.520
How could I blame him?

30:52.160 --> 30:56.480
Without Ji Ling, there would be no peace.

31:07.280 --> 31:08.280
Ji Ling.

31:08.960 --> 31:12.600
You are the real Dragon Deity
to the people.

31:14.680 --> 31:17.640
Let's drink to the former Dragon Deity,

31:20.640 --> 31:21.680
Ji Ling.

31:28.920 --> 31:30.480
To Master Bai Ze.

31:33.200 --> 31:36.200
To Si Feng.

31:39.440 --> 31:42.720
To all those who died to save the world.

31:44.880 --> 31:48.360
And to the hardships we shared

31:48.440 --> 31:50.520
and to Wu Shiguang for becoming a dragon.

31:50.600 --> 31:52.040
And to…

31:52.680 --> 31:55.360
To… To our precious friendship.

31:56.560 --> 31:59.960
You sure know how to cozy up
to people, you little weasel.

32:00.040 --> 32:03.680
Hold on tight to the Shilin Sect token,
or you'll be shattered.

32:17.760 --> 32:18.840
Wuyi.

32:30.320 --> 32:32.400
Wu Shiguang, Li Jie, and the others

32:33.760 --> 32:38.120
are drinking and celebrating
under the golden-scale wood.

32:39.800 --> 32:41.000
Celebrating?

32:42.760 --> 32:44.280
What I mean is,

32:45.600 --> 32:49.240
it's not just about celebrating
the death of Jiu Ying.

32:50.440 --> 32:51.600
On top of that,

32:52.840 --> 32:54.240
more importantly,

32:55.880 --> 32:57.960
they are commemorating Ji Ling.

32:58.800 --> 33:02.240
The golden-scale wood
is full of ribbons for Ji Ling

33:02.320 --> 33:04.480
from demon hunters and common people.

33:05.960 --> 33:07.760
Don't you want to check it out?

33:09.760 --> 33:10.800
No.

33:17.680 --> 33:18.640
Wuyi.

33:19.960 --> 33:22.200
I thought I gave you my heart.

33:23.040 --> 33:27.120
But your true heart
was Jiu Ying's spirit fragment.

33:28.760 --> 33:31.160
The last head of Jiu Ying was destroyed.

33:33.200 --> 33:35.680
And all the fragments faded away.

33:36.320 --> 33:38.160
You would have died.

33:42.200 --> 33:46.720
But Ji Ling kept you alive
with his dragon scale.

33:47.840 --> 33:51.720
He surely wishes for you
to live on, happy and well.

33:54.640 --> 33:57.440
I don't know what else I can do for you.

34:00.720 --> 34:05.520
But are you going to stay here forever?

34:07.080 --> 34:09.120
If Ji Ling could see you right now,

34:13.080 --> 34:16.120
he would never want you to be like this.

34:17.560 --> 34:19.520
Come back to the Formless Moon with me.

34:22.120 --> 34:23.719
I'll keep you company.

34:58.760 --> 34:59.920
Wangyan.

36:00.480 --> 36:01.680
Disturbing, huh?

36:02.680 --> 36:03.880
Painful, huh?

36:06.320 --> 36:07.480
Jiu Ying.

36:10.160 --> 36:12.200
You're still alive.

36:13.000 --> 36:15.720
As long as you're alive, I'll survive.

36:16.360 --> 36:20.400
What I put in your heart
wasn't just my spirit fragment.

36:20.480 --> 36:22.160
There's also the Oracle Stone.

36:43.360 --> 36:45.800
I wasted half of my sacred power

36:45.880 --> 36:50.520
to cut out a small piece
of the indestructible Oracle Stone.

37:22.000 --> 37:26.000
As long as the stone endures,
I shall not die.

37:28.920 --> 37:31.840
Guess why I wrapped Wu Wangyan's heart

37:31.920 --> 37:34.920
around my spirit fragment I left in you.

37:35.600 --> 37:38.040
Because it's my biggest secret.

37:38.120 --> 37:41.600
This secret must remain
undetectable to anyone.

37:41.680 --> 37:44.360
Now Ji Ling is dead.

37:44.920 --> 37:47.240
Wu Shiguang has become
the new Dragon Deity.

37:47.320 --> 37:50.040
No one in this world
will remember and honor Ji Ling

37:50.120 --> 37:51.320
except for you.

37:51.840 --> 37:55.720
And this longing
will be your eternal shackles,

37:55.800 --> 37:58.480
torturing you forever.

38:00.080 --> 38:02.480
Why don't we set you free now?

38:02.560 --> 38:04.760
Hand over your physical form.

38:04.840 --> 38:09.720
Let your heart fly to the one
you love and stay with him.

38:33.000 --> 38:34.400
Come with me.

38:57.880 --> 38:59.440
He's not gone.

39:00.600 --> 39:02.360
He's in my heart,

39:03.840 --> 39:05.400
keeping me company all along.

39:09.400 --> 39:11.840
You can wear human skin to look like him.

39:12.880 --> 39:16.960
But you'll never have his loving eyes.

39:19.840 --> 39:22.480
He loves me and the people.

39:24.000 --> 39:25.120
So,

39:27.520 --> 39:29.400
I won't let you ruin

39:31.320 --> 39:33.560
the world he has been guarding.

40:14.760 --> 40:16.040
We need to talk.

40:16.120 --> 40:18.400
Wait for me to come back.

40:19.880 --> 40:20.960
What's wrong with you?

40:21.040 --> 40:23.880
You're too busy to even
talk to your brother?

40:23.960 --> 40:25.720
What are you talking about?

40:25.800 --> 40:28.000
You're the Dragon Deity now.

40:28.080 --> 40:29.640
Everyone listens to you.

40:30.680 --> 40:33.120
What about me? What do I do?

40:33.200 --> 40:35.360
-What do you mean?
-You dog…

40:36.040 --> 40:39.160
When you're riding high,
don't ditch your pack.

40:40.040 --> 40:41.920
You won't even let me stay
in the Cosmic Pouch.

40:42.000 --> 40:45.440
I have nowhere to go here
with terrifying formations everywhere.

40:46.160 --> 40:47.800
What am I doing here?

40:48.560 --> 40:50.520
We ran into danger
several times out there.

40:50.600 --> 40:52.160
Have you forgotten?

40:52.680 --> 40:53.800
It's for your own good.

40:53.880 --> 40:56.360
You're not a weasel.
You're an ungrateful brat.

40:56.440 --> 40:59.000
I'm not afraid of danger. I'm afraid of…

40:59.080 --> 41:02.080
Enough. You're obviously still drunk.

41:02.160 --> 41:03.280
We'll talk later.

41:14.560 --> 41:15.680
What's wrong?

41:16.640 --> 41:19.080
The last Dragon Deity's Power from Chi Wen

41:19.640 --> 41:23.240
took Ji Ling's heart stone
to the Dragon Abyss.

41:23.840 --> 41:28.560
He said that the heart stone
contains all the memories of Ji Ling.

41:30.480 --> 41:32.480
Maybe thousands of years later,

41:33.760 --> 41:35.200
it can cultivate into human form.

41:39.960 --> 41:41.000
That's great.

41:43.280 --> 41:44.920
Humans are mortal.

41:45.520 --> 41:47.320
I can't wait that long.

41:51.440 --> 41:52.840
But you can.

41:54.680 --> 41:56.360
If you see him,

41:57.600 --> 41:59.360
tell him

42:00.320 --> 42:04.720
that I've figured out who I am.

42:33.200 --> 42:35.760
Look. So sparkling.

42:36.520 --> 42:39.920
Doesn't it look like our former home?

42:44.120 --> 42:45.920
I remember that I liked

42:47.280 --> 42:51.120
waiting for you by the water
in the illusion.

42:52.840 --> 42:54.160
This time,

42:55.520 --> 42:58.480
let me wait for you by the water.

43:00.760 --> 43:02.480
I'll be back in just a few days.

43:05.240 --> 43:06.960
That's long enough.

43:18.800 --> 43:20.440
This is…

43:22.400 --> 43:26.560
I added my dragon scale to it.

43:41.360 --> 43:43.080
Impressive craftsmanship.

43:48.720 --> 43:50.560
You once said

43:52.400 --> 43:53.760
that two people

43:56.240 --> 43:58.320
are like two rivers.

44:00.320 --> 44:02.040
They converge

44:04.000 --> 44:06.360
and change each other's course.

44:08.800 --> 44:12.680
But it seems our fates
are headed in directions

44:13.240 --> 44:16.600
that will never let us
grow old together like normal people.

44:17.720 --> 44:21.440
It's fine, as long

44:21.960 --> 44:24.320
as I can stay with you forever.

44:33.000 --> 44:33.960
Wangyan.

44:38.520 --> 44:39.680
Marry me.

45:50.520 --> 45:51.520
Sisters.

45:52.440 --> 45:57.160
We carried out many tasks
assigned by Jiu Ying,

45:59.440 --> 46:03.200
causing a lot of tragedy
beyond redemption.

46:07.520 --> 46:09.960
Wangyan. Let's go.

46:26.960 --> 46:31.800
I want to give it my all
to redeem the errors I once made.

46:35.040 --> 46:37.000
But it's just my choice.

46:38.960 --> 46:41.600
You've dedicated everything
to the Formless Moon.

46:41.680 --> 46:46.240
It's time to start your own lives
and pursue true freedom.

46:47.080 --> 46:50.160
But I don't know what I want, either.

46:50.760 --> 46:53.200
I think I'm used to this lifestyle.

46:53.720 --> 46:56.240
I'm used to carrying out missions.

46:56.760 --> 46:58.720
Instead of searching aimlessly,

46:58.800 --> 47:01.600
why don't we make amends with you?

47:02.200 --> 47:03.360
That's right.

47:03.440 --> 47:05.560
We are sisters
who share honor and disgrace.

47:06.200 --> 47:07.880
We should stand by each other.

47:10.680 --> 47:11.520
Wangyan.

47:21.120 --> 47:25.400
Formless Moon, submit to me.
